SortAlgDemo

Class SortVisualizer_UIColor

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.plaf.metal.MetalTheme
      • javax.swing.plaf.metal.DefaultMetalTheme
        • SortAlgDemo.SortVisualizer_UIColor

  • public class SortVisualizer_UIColor
extends javax.swing.plaf.metal.DefaultMetalTheme
    The SortVisualizer_UIColor class is the color theme of the GUI. It controls the coloring of the software outlook.
